{"tid":1945992,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"報道刪武肺 中國竄改播毒史","createTime":"2020-03-27T11:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T11:48:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"41173766adf6473087b2095b22fc34279b1072d9","tid":1945992,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:20:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200327/HQLJQVJDCVUHDDKBX7WOQJIY6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200327%2FHQLJQVJDCVUHDDKBX7WOQJIY6E%2F&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=4ec67fa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200327%2FHQLJQVJDCVUHDDKBX7WOQJIY6E%2F&h=a33b23fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200327/HQLJQVJDCVUHDDKBX7WOQJIY6E/</a><br />\n<br />\n報道刪武肺 中國竄改播毒史<br />\n<br />\n中國國家衞生健康委員會上月8日將武漢肺炎暫時命名為「新型冠狀病毒肺炎」，但此前一直叫「武漢肺炎」。中國近日極力反對武漢肺炎之名，有網媒發現中國官方正竄改歷史，將2月8日前提及的武漢肺炎的報道，全部改名為「與冠狀病毒相關的不明肺炎」。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter賬戶「LIFETIME視界」25日晚間發文指出，中共正開始大規模「修改」武漢肺炎疫情歷史。《環球時報》英文網站偷偷地將1月18日一則報道的標題，由「武漢肺炎」改成「不明與冠狀病毒相關的肺炎」。該帖文同時發佈了有關報道的兩張截圖，可見到兩者雖然刊登日期及內容相同，但其中一篇的標題為「Wuhan pneumonia：China confirms 4 new cases，2 deaths」，另一篇的則為「Novel coronavirus-related pneumonia：China confirms 4 new cases，2 deaths」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200327/large/1585245966_05e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200327%2Flarge%2F1585245966_05e2.jpg&h=4914d5e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報道原本的「武肺」標題（左圖）被改為「不明肺炎」（右圖）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出口試劑錯誤率高<br />\n<br />\n歷史有假，不料內地連供應外國武漢肺炎的試劑都出現問題。捷克向中國採購武漢肺炎快篩試劑，一度傳出錯誤率高達80%，後來捷克衞生官員澄清說，錯誤率並非高達80%，而是20%到30%。西班牙當地媒體亦發現，中國的試劑準確率本應超過80%，但現時準確率竟低於30%。西班牙衞生局回應指，已經將9,000支有問題的試劑退回中國，並要求更換新試劑。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"b3de1c6fe38e97f8f30673c8511bfe98efce59be","tid":1945992,"uid":221419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:21:59.000Z","msg":"丁蟹.gif"},{"pid":"f53915c06d0fdcb9638da75981291e771ceabd86","tid":1945992,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd13b2c64b0d4c24c5c1b26c741227141be640b","tid":1945992,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5148de1520bce10a70048916a5f67f98c5be44d5","tid"